com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.wizard

Class SCUIWizardEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.wizard.SCUIWizardEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISCUIWizardEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SCUIWizardPageHolder, SCUIWizardRuleHolder

    public class SCUIWizardEntity
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISCUIWizardEntity
    Super class for all Wizard Entities. Entities currently constitute Pages and Rules. Any new entity type may subclass this and with a suitable model definition can fit into the existing scheme of things within the wizard. asmishra
